    <item>
      <title>据称韦丹塔债权人将于 2 月开会批准拆分</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/vedanta-creditors-said-to-meet-in-february-to-approve-split</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韦丹塔有限公司的债权人将于下个月召开会议，对将这家庞大的印度矿业集团拆分为至少五个不同业务的计划做出最终裁决，这是数月来简化集团结构和管理债务负担的努力的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/vedanta-creditors-said-to-meet-in-february-to-approve-split</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 02:37:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税风险迫在眉睫，利洁时计划提高美国产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/reckitt-aims-to-boost-us-production-as-risk-of-tariffs-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[利洁时公司 (Reckitt Benckiser Plc) 在美国销售的产品中，有五分之二以上依赖进口，在即将上任的总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 威胁征收关税之际，该公司计划提高在美国的生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/reckitt-aims-to-boost-us-production-as-risk-of-tariffs-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 02:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能推动英伟达相关股票上涨，黄光裕股价涨幅有望消退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/huang-bump-seen-fading-for-nvidia-linked-stocks-riding-ai-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管提及与 Nvidia Corp. 的联系仍会引发全球各地公司股价的大幅上涨，但这种涨势可能是短暂的，一些投资者正在质疑光环效应是否正在消退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/huang-bump-seen-fading-for-nvidia-linked-stocks-riding-ai-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 02:07:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场等待美国 CPI 测试，比特币受到科技股的启发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bitcoin-btc-nasdaq-100-correlation-at-two-year-high-before-us-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币与美国科技股指数之间的相关性已达到两年来的最高水平，这表明股市对周三晚些时候公布的美国通胀数据的反应可能为数字代币定下基调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bitcoin-btc-nasdaq-100-correlation-at-two-year-high-before-us-cpi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 01:36:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
